nnoremap <leader><space> :nohlsearch<CR>

" Remapping escape to jk
inoremap jk <Esc>
vnoremap jk <Esc>

" Tab moves to next window within pane
map <Tab> <C-w>w

" | Creates a vertical split and moves there
nmap <Bar> <C-w>v<C-W><Right>

" - creates a horizontal split and moves there
nmap - <C-w>s<C-W><Down>
